description: AMUNDI GLOBAL INFRASTRUCTURE - UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the evolution of the Solactive Global Infrastructure Low Earnings Volatility Index, net dividend reinvested (net return), whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit - in a single transaction - from an exposure to the listed infrastructure companies worldwide with the most stable earnings growth. Please refer to the fund prospectus for more details on the index rules.
name: Amundi Global Infrastructure UCITS ETF (C)
